        <div class="content">
            <!-- TYPES AND STAGING -->
            <section id="types" class="section">
                <h2>Aggressive Lymphoma Types & Staging</h2>
                
                <div class="info-box">
                    <p><strong>Note:</strong> In the hospital, you'll primarily see aggressive lymphomas. Less aggressive forms are typically managed outpatient.</p>
                </div>

                <h3>Types of Aggressive Lymphoma</h3>
                
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Type</th>
                        <th>Key Features</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>DLBCL</strong><br>(Diffuse Large B-Cell Lymphoma)</td>
                        <td>Most common aggressive lymphoma; rapid growth; potentially curable with chemotherapy</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>HGBCL</strong><br>(High-Grade B-Cell Lymphoma)</td>
                        <td>Includes "double-hit" and "triple-hit" lymphomas with MYC rearrangements</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Burkitt Lymphoma</strong></td>
                        <td>Highly aggressive; MYC translocation; requires intensive chemotherapy (DA-EPOCH-R)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Primary Mediastinal B-Cell Lymphoma</strong></td>
                        <td>Arises in mediastinum; often in young women; good prognosis with DA-EPOCH-R</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>CNS Lymphoma</strong></td>
                        <td>Primary brain lymphoma; requires high-dose methotrexate-based therapy</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

                <h3>IPI Score (International Prognostic Index)</h3>
                
                <div class="mnemonic">
                    <strong>Mnemonic: APLES</strong> (remember "apples" for lymphoma staging)
                </div>

                <div class="score-box">
                    <h4>IPI Risk Factors (1 point each):</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>A</strong>ge >60 years</li>
                        <li><strong>P</strong>erformance status (ECOG) ≥2</li>
                        <li><strong>L</strong>DH elevated (>upper limit of normal)</li>
                        <li><strong>E</strong>xtranodal sites >1</li>
                        <li><strong>S</strong>tage III or IV disease</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <p style="margin-top:15px;"><strong>Interpretation:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Low risk (0-1):</strong> ~70-90% 5-year survival</li>
                        <li><strong>Low-intermediate (2):</strong> ~50-70% 5-year survival</li>
                        <li><strong>High-intermediate (3):</strong> ~30-50% 5-year survival</li>
                        <li><strong>High risk (4-5):</strong> ~15-30% 5-year survival</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <p><strong>Quick IPI Calculator:</strong> Use MDCalc for easy calculation</p>
                </div>

                <h3>Double-Hit and Triple-Hit Lymphoma</h3>

                <div class="warning-box">
                    <h4>⚠️ High-Grade B-Cell Lymphoma (HGBCL)</h4>
                    <p>Characterized by rearrangements in <strong>MYC</strong> plus <strong>BCL-2</strong> and/or <strong>BCL-6</strong></p>
                    
                    <ul style="margin-top:10px;">
                        <li><strong>Double-Hit:</strong> MYC + (BCL-2 OR BCL-6)</li>
                        <li><strong>Triple-Hit:</strong> MYC + BCL-2 + BCL-6</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <p style="margin-top:10px;"><strong>Treatment:</strong> Requires intensive therapy (DA-EPOCH-R), NOT standard R-CHOP</p>
                </div>

                <h3>Hans Algorithm</h3>
                
                <div class="info-box">
                    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Sub-classifies DLBCL based on cell of origin using immunohistochemistry</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>GCB (Germinal Center B-cell):</strong> Better prognosis</li>
                        <li><strong>Non-GCB (Activated B-cell):</strong> Worse prognosis</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Hans Algorithm Flowchart -->
                <div style="background: white; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 30px; margin: 20px 0;">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 800 400" style="width: 100%; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; display: block;">
                        <!-- CD10 box -->
                        <rect x="50" y="150" width="120" height="80" fill="#2c5aa0" stroke="#1e3a8a" stroke-width="2" rx="8"/>
                        <text x="110" y="195" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="24" font-weight="bold">CD10</text>
                        
                        <!-- CD10+ arrow to GCB -->
                        <path d="M 170 170 L 280 90" stroke="#2c5aa0" stroke-width="3" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrowblue)"/>
                        <text x="200" y="120" font-size="20" font-weight="bold">+</text>
                        
                        <!-- GCB box (top) -->
                        <rect x="280" y="50" width="120" height="80" fill="#93c5fd" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2" rx="8"/>
                        <text x="340" y="95" text-anchor="middle" fill="#1e3a8a" font-size="22" font-weight="bold">GCB</text>
                        
                        <!-- CD10- arrow to BCL6 -->
                        <path d="M 170 210 L 280 240" stroke="#2c5aa0" stroke-width="3" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrowblue)"/>
                        <text x="200" y="235" font-size="20" font-weight="bold">−</text>
                        
                        <!-- BCL6 box -->
                        <rect x="280" y="200" width="120" height="80" fill="#2c5aa0" stroke="#1e3a8a" stroke-width="2" rx="8"/>
                        <text x="340" y="245" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="22" font-weight="bold">BCL6</text>
                        
                        <!-- BCL6+ arrow to MUM1 -->
                        <path d="M 400 220 L 490 160" stroke="#2c5aa0" stroke-width="3" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrowblue)"/>
                        <text x="430" y="180" font-size="20" font-weight="bold">+</text>
                        
                        <!-- MUM1 box -->
                        <rect x="490" y="120" width="120" height="80" fill="#2c5aa0" stroke="#1e3a8a" stroke-width="2" rx="8"/>
                        <text x="550" y="165" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="22" font-weight="bold">MUM1</text>
                        
                        <!-- MUM1+ arrow to Non-GCB (top right) -->
                        <path d="M 610 140 L 680 90" stroke="#2c5aa0" stroke-width="3" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrowgray)"/>
                        <text x="630" y="105" font-size="20" font-weight="bold">+</text>
                        
                        <!-- Non-GCB box (top right) -->
                        <rect x="650" y="50" width="140" height="80" fill="#9ca3af" stroke="#4b5563" stroke-width="2" rx="8"/>
                        <text x="720" y="95" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="20" font-weight="bold">Non-GCB</text>
                        
                        <!-- MUM1- arrow to GCB (middle right) -->
                        <path d="M 610 180 L 680 200" stroke="#2c5aa0" stroke-width="3" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrowblue2)"/>
                        <text x="630" y="200" font-size="20" font-weight="bold">−</text>
                        
                        <!-- GCB box (middle right) -->
                        <rect x="650" y="160" width="140" height="80" fill="#93c5fd" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2" rx="8"/>
                        <text x="720" y="205" text-anchor="middle" fill="#1e3a8a" font-size="22" font-weight="bold">GCB</text>
                        
                        <!-- BCL6- arrow to Non-GCB (bottom) -->
                        <path d="M 400 260 L 490 320" stroke="#2c5aa0" stroke-width="3" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrowgray)"/>
                        <text x="430" y="300" font-size="20" font-weight="bold">−</text>
                        
                        <!-- Non-GCB box (bottom) -->
                        <rect x="490" y="280" width="140" height="80" fill="#9ca3af" stroke="#4b5563" stroke-width="2" rx="8"/>
                        <text x="560" y="325" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="20" font-weight="bold">Non-GCB</text>
                        
                        <!-- Arrow markers -->
                        <defs>
                            <marker id="arrowblue" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="10" refX="9" refY="3" orient="auto" markerUnits="strokeWidth">
                                <path d="M0,0 L0,6 L9,3 z" fill="#2c5aa0" />
                            </marker>
                            <marker id="arrowblue2" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="10" refX="9" refY="3" orient="auto" markerUnits="strokeWidth">
                                <path d="M0,0 L0,6 L9,3 z" fill="#2c5aa0" />
                            </marker>
                            <marker id="arrowgray" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="10" refX="9" refY="3" orient="auto" markerUnits="strokeWidth">
                                <path d="M0,0 L0,6 L9,3 z" fill="#2c5aa0" />
                            </marker>
                        </defs>
                    </svg>
                    
                    <div style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background: #f0f9ff; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 3px solid #2563eb;">
                        <p style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px;">Quick Reference:</p>
                        <ul style="margin-left: 20px; font-size: 0.9em;">
                            <li><strong>CD10+</strong> → GCB (stop here, best prognosis)</li>
                            <li><strong>CD10−, BCL6−</strong> → Non-GCB</li>
                            <li><strong>CD10−, BCL6+, MUM1+</strong> → Non-GCB</li>
                            <li><strong>CD10−, BCL6+, MUM1−</strong> → GCB</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- FIRST-LINE THERAPY -->
